to marry him, but she won't.

344
00:33:24,564 --> 00:33:27,533
- How come?
- Too scared.

345
00:33:27,634 --> 00:33:30,535
<i>May, June might think that's a little personal.</i>

346
00:33:30,637 --> 00:33:33,697
<i>Hell, I'll tell any folk that'll listen</i>
